From Thomas Beagle Subject Re WINQVTNET with NDIS on Token Ring In article A Wim Van Holder writes Is it possible to use WinQVT Net on a machine that uses NDIS to connect to a Token Ring I tried it with older versions but got an invalid packet class error or something the like How are you attempting to do that Are you using the DIS PKT program This provides a packet driver on top of the NDIS driver Thomas Beagle Work o Technical Writer Home , Wellington, NZ Hound for hire Will work for dog biscuits